{
  "schema_version": 1,
  "name": "Fathom Brick",
  "mood": "Foundation",
  "engines": [
    "Obrix"
  ],
  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "OBRIX through Aquatic Chain with Fathom as the primary character effect. Sub-oscillator (src1Type=0, sine) paired with noise source creates a foundational weight. Fathom at Character 0.0 (maximum deep emphasis) compresses this foundation into maximum density and low-mid body. Drift minimal — 2 voices, small depth — the brickwork should be stable. Tide off. Reef at size 0.4, decay 0.65 — just enough space to breathe. This preset demonstrates Fathom's ability to create the impression of mass in a signal — OBRIX already has density, Fathom concentrates it into a brick.",
